# 09 - Story Generator (Multi-Agent with Profiles)
# Creative writing with writer and editor personas using different models

NAME story-generator
INPUT genre DEFAULT "science fiction"
INPUT theme
INPUT length DEFAULT "short story"

AGENT writer FROM agents/creative-writer.md REQUIRES "creative"
AGENT editor FROM agents/editor.md REQUIRES "reasoning-heavy"

GOAL concept "One paragraph concept for $genre $length about $theme. Focus on hook and conflict."
GOAL draft "Write $length (500-800 words). Focus on pacing over description." USING writer
GOAL critique "List top 3 improvements only." USING editor
GOAL revise "Apply critique. Minor edits only. Save to story-output.md." USING writer

RUN create USING concept, draft, critique, revise
